{
  "page": "A certain man",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\"><img alt=\"Myr.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f1/Myr.svg/50px-Myr.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f1/Myr.svg/75px-Myr.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f1/Myr.svg/100px-Myr.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">A certain man</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\"><img alt=\"Myr.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f1/Myr.svg/50px-Myr.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f1/Myr.svg/75px-Myr.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f1/Myr.svg/100px-Myr.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\">Myrish</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Played by</span></th><td>\nHarold James McMullan</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">TV series</span></th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>: <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_3\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 3\">Season 3</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>During his childhood, <a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a> was the victim of <b>a certain man</b>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Magic\" title=\"Magic\">sorcerer</a> who <a href=\"/index.php/Eunuch\" title=\"Eunuch\">gelded him</a> in a <a href=\"/index.php/Demon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Demon\">demonic</a> ritual. The sorcerer's true name is not mentioned.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> In the television adapation <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>, the sorcerer is portrayed by Harold James McMullan.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Behind_the_scenes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Behind the scenes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_certain_man&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Flame_and_ShadowNG.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d1/Flame_and_ShadowNG.png/350px-Flame_and_ShadowNG.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"252\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d1/Flame_and_ShadowNG.png/525px-Flame_and_ShadowNG.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d1/Flame_and_ShadowNG.png/700px-Flame_and_ShadowNG.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Flame_and_ShadowNG.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A <a href=\"/index.php/Bloodmagic\" title=\"Bloodmagic\">bloodmagic</a> ritual brazier, by Nicholas Gregory © FFG</div></div></div>\n<p>When Varys was an orphan boy, he was apprenticed to a traveling <a href=\"/index.php/Mummer\" title=\"Mummer\">folly</a>. The folly's master owned a fat little <a href=\"/index.php/Watercraft\" title=\"Watercraft\">cog</a>, and they sailed up and down the <a href=\"/index.php/Narrow_sea\" title=\"Narrow sea\">narrow sea</a> performing in all the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a>, and from time to time in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/King%E2%80%99s_Landing\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King’s Landing\">King’s Landing</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>One day at <a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\">Myr</a>, a certain man came to the folly. After the performance, he made an offer for young Varys that his master found too tempting to refuse. As he was <a href=\"/index.php/Slavery\" title=\"Slavery\">sold</a>, Varys was in terror, afraid that the man meant to use him as he had heard men used small boys. However, the only part of Varys the man had need of was his manhood. The man gave Varys a potion that made him powerless to move or speak, but did nothing to dull his senses as his manhood was cut off at the stem with a long hooked <a href=\"/index.php/Knife\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Knife\">blade</a>, then burnt in a brazier in a <a href=\"/index.php/Bloodmagic\" title=\"Bloodmagic\">bloodmagic</a> ritual while the sorcerer chanted. Varys saw the flames turn blue and heard a voice within them answer the man's call, but he did not understand the words they spoke.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>With the ritual complete, the man had no further use for Varys and tossed him out on the streets. The mummers' ship had sailed away by then, so Varys asked the man what he should do. The sorcerer replied that he supposed Varys should die. To spite him, Varys vowed to live.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_certain_man&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_certain_man&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> asks Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_whisperers\" title=\"Master of whisperers\">master of whisperers</a>, how he became a <a href=\"/index.php/Eunuch\" title=\"Eunuch\">eunuch</a>, but Varys refuses to answer.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Some months later, while Tyrion and Varys discuss the <a href=\"/index.php/Shadow_assassin\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Shadow assassin\">mysterious deaths</a> of King <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>'s enemies, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Cortnay_Penrose\" title=\"Cortnay Penrose\">Cortnay Penrose</a> and King <a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly Baratheon</a>, Varys suggests that they were performed by <a href=\"/index.php/Magic\" title=\"Magic\">magic</a>. Tyrion is scornful of the idea, so Varys tells the story of his gelding and the ritual, referring to his mutilator as \"a certain man\". Varys explains that since that day, he has hated magic and all magic practitioners, and it is for this reason he opposes Stannis.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_certain_man&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Tyrion:</b> <a href=\"/index.php/Dwarf\" title=\"Dwarf\">Dwarfs</a> are a jape of the <a href=\"/index.php/Gods\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Gods\">gods</a>... but men make <a href=\"/index.php/Eunuch\" title=\"Eunuch\">eunuchs</a>. Who cut you, <a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a>? When and why? Who are you, truly?<br />\n<b>Varys:</b> You are kind to ask, my lord, but my tale is long and sad, and we have <a href=\"/index.php/Treason\" title=\"Treason\">treasons</a> to discuss.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a>, to <a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I still dream of that night, my lord. Not of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sorcerer\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sorcerer\">sorcerer</a>, nor his blade, nor even the way my manhood shriveled as it burned. I dream of the voice. The voice from the flames. Was it a <a href=\"/index.php/God\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"God\">god</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Demon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Demon\">demon</a>, some conjurer's trick? I could not tell you, and I know all the tricks. All I can say for a certainty is that he called it, and it answered, and since that day I have hated <a href=\"/index.php/Magic\" title=\"Magic\">magic</a> and all those who practice it. If Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis</a> is one such, I mean to see him dead.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a>, to <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_scenes\">Behind the scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_certain_man&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In an interview, <a href=\"/index.php/George_R.R._Martin\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"George R.R. Martin\">George R.R. Martin</a> suggested that the passage of time may have colored Varys's memory of the events.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_certain_man&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.5</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_44\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 44\">Chapter 44</a>, Tyrion X.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_8\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 8\">Chapter 8</a>, Tyrion II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><span class=\"citation audio-visual\">&#32;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/rgGOiUxxA8k?si=BmKERIEqYRBcfuUn&amp;t=327\"><i>Chalkskin 10: George R.R. Martin (part two)</i></a>.&#32;April 23, 2016.&#32;Event occurs at 5:27<span class=\"printonly\">.&#32;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"https://youtu.be/rgGOiUxxA8k?si=BmKERIEqYRBcfuUn&amp;t=327\">https://youtu.be/rgGOiUxxA8k?si=BmKERIEqYRBcfuUn&amp;t=327</a></span>.</span><span class=\"Z3988\" title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Chalkskin+10%3A+George+R.R.+Martin+%28part+two%29&amp;rft.date=April+23%2C+2016&amp;rft.pages=Event+occurs+at+5%3A27&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrgGOiUxxA8k%3Fsi%3DBmKERIEqYRBcfuUn%26t%3D327&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:A_certain_man\"><span style=\"display: none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404041648\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.085 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.257 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1536/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 22636/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 11884/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2447/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3777/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.150/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.45 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  242.428      1 -total\n 88.92%  215.576      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 88.18%  213.778      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.35%   25.100     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  5.35%   12.969      8 Template:Ref\n  4.95%   12.007      1 Template:References\n  3.82%    9.249      1 Template:Cite_video\n  3.31%    8.021      1 Template:Citation/core\n  3.18%    7.708      8 Template:Ref/core\n  2.52%    6.117      2 Template:Infobox_label\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:16940-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404041647 and revision id 317357\n -->\n",
